     __________________________________________________________________

   Select the dates for your report. Valid dates run from 2/1/96 through
   yesterday's date. Leaving the start and/or end date empty will
   substitute yesterday's date for the unspecified date(s). The time
   required for the report to be generated is proportional to the number
   of days of data requested.

